by him.

77
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:51,826
Increasingly, he became aware
that his phenomenal sense of smell...

78
00:09:51,919 --> 00:09:54,270
was a gift that had been give to him...

79
00:09:54,646 --> 00:09:56,235
and him alone.

80
00:10:04,249 --> 00:10:07,562
When Jean-Baptiste did
finally learn to speak...

81
00:10:07,822 --> 00:10:09,881
